                    td.value #{project.order.rate?"" + project.order.rate.amount + " €": "Waiting for rate."}
                  tr.separator-small
                    td(col-span='2')
                  tr
                    td.desc.text-shadow-3doers Total Price:
                    td.value
                      h3.normal #{project.order.rate?(parseFloat(project.order.totalPrice) + project.order.rate.amount):project.order.totalPrice} €
                  tr
                    td(colspan='2')
                      p.final-price *Final price will include a shipping fee and will be calculated once the order has been accepted by a printer.
        .row
          .col-md-3
            .form-group
              a(href='#', data-toggle='modal', data-target='#orderModal') Cancel order

              .modal.fade(id='orderModal', role='dialog')
                .modal-dialog.modal-md
                  .modal-content
                    .modal-header
                      button.close(data-dismiss='modal')
                        span &times;
                      h4.modal-title &nbsp;
                    .modal-body
                      p
                        | Once deleted the order won't be accesible anymore.
                        br
                        | Do you want to proceed?
                      br
                      form(action='/project/delete/#{ project._id }', method='post')
                        .row
                          .col-md-5
                            .form-group
                              a.btn.btn-xlg.btn-block.btn-green-inverse(data-dismiss='modal', href='#') Undo
                          .col-md-7
                            .form-group
                              button.btn.btn-xlg.btn-block.btn-green(type='submit') CANCEL ORDER

          .col-md-4.col-md-offset-5
            form#hidden-pay-form(action="/project/pay/#{project.id}", method="post")
              .form-group
                button.btn.btn-xlg.btn-block.btn-green(href='#', type='submit') PROCEED WITH PAYMENT
            p.text-muted.text-light.text-xsmall The payment will be secured on 3Doers account and won’t be released to the printer until the order has been completed and delivered to you.

